{"text_id":218983,"tokens":["A"," gesture"," is"," a"," movement"," of"," the"," body",","," especially"," of"," the"," hands",","," that"," is"," used"," to"," convey"," meaning"," or"," to"," draw"," attention","."," A"," gesture"," can"," be"," a"," simple"," movement",","," such"," as"," a"," wave"," or"," a"," handshake",","," or"," it"," can"," be"," a"," more"," complex"," movement",","," such"," as"," a"," dance"," or"," a"," sign"," language",".","\n","The"," use"," of"," gestures"," is"," a"," common"," feature"," of"," human"," communication","."," It"," is"," a"," way"," for"," people"," to"," express"," themselves"," and"," to"," convey"," meaning","."," Gest","ures"," can"," be"," used"," to"," communicate"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," emotions"," and"," ideas",","," and"," they"," can"," be"," used"," in"," a"," variety"," of"," contexts",","," such"," as"," during"," a"," conversation",","," a"," presentation",","," or"," a"," performance",".","\n","One"," of"," the"," most"," common"," types"," of"," gestures"," is"," the"," obscene"," gesture","."," This"," is"," a"," gesture"," that"," is"," used"," to"," convey"," a"," sexual"," or"," offensive"," message","."," It"," is"," often"," used"," as"," a"," form"," of"," harassment"," or"," to"," express"," anger"," or"," frustration",".","\n","There"," are"," many"," examples"," of"," obscene"," gestures"," that"," have"," been"," used"," throughout"," history","."," Some"," examples"," include",":","\n","-"," The"," middle"," finger",":"," This"," is"," a"," gesture"," in"," which"," the"," index"," finger"," and"," the"," middle"," finger"," are"," extended",","," with"," the"," middle"," finger"," being"," the"," dominant"," one","."," It"," is"," often"," used"," to"," convey"," a"," negative"," message",","," such"," as"," to"," express"," anger"," or"," frustration",".","\n","-"," The"," thumb"," to"," the"," nose",":"," This"," is"," a"," gesture"," in"," which"," the"," thumb"," is"," extended"," and"," the"," index"," finger"," is"," pointed"," towards"," the"," nose","."," It"," is"," often"," used"," to"," convey"," a"," mocking"," or"," disrespectful"," message",".","\n","-"," The"," finger"," to"," the"," eye",":"," This"," is"," a"," gesture"," in"," which"," the"," index"," finger"," is"," pointed"," towards"," the"," eye","."," It"," is"," often"," used"," to"," convey"," a"," threatening"," or"," aggressive"," message",".","\n","There"," are"," many"," other"," examples"," of"," obscene"," gestures"," that"," have"," been"," used"," throughout"," history","."," Some"," of"," these"," gestures"," may"," have"," been"," used"," to"," convey"," a"," positive"," message",","," such"," as"," a"," sign"," of"," affection"," or"," a"," promise"," of"," good"," luck","."," However",","," many"," of"," these"," gestures"," were"," used"," to"," convey"," a"," negative"," message",","," such"," as"," a"," sign"," of"," anger"," or"," disrespect",".","\n","It"," is"," important"," to"," note"," that"," the"," use"," of"," obscene"," gestures"," can"," be"," offensive"," and"," harmful",","," and"," it"," is"," important"," to"," be"," aware"," of"," the"," potential"," consequences"," of"," using"," such"," gestures","."," It"," is"," also"," important"," to"," be"," respectful"," of"," the"," cultural"," and"," personal"," context"," in"," which"," a"," gesture"," is"," being"," used",","," and"," to"," avoid"," using"," gestures"," that"," may"," be"," considered"," offensive"," or"," harmful"," in"," that"," context",".","\n","The"," question"," of"," how"," we"," know"," what"," these"," gestures"," looked"," like"," is"," a"," complex"," one","."," There"," are"," many"," ways"," in"," which"," we"," can"," learn"," about"," the"," gestures"," used"," by"," different"," cultures"," and"," societies","."," One"," way"," is"," through"," the"," study"," of"," art"," and"," literature",","," as"," these"," sources"," often"," contain"," depictions"," of"," gestures"," and"," their"," meanings","."," Another"," way"," is"," through"," the"," study"," of"," history"," and"," anthropology",","," as"," these"," fields"," often"," focus"," on"," the"," study"," of"," gesture"," and"," its"," role"," in"," different"," cultures",".","\n","Another"," way"," we"," can"," learn"," about"," the"," gestures"," used"," by"," different"," cultures"," is"," through"," the"," study"," of"," language","."," Many"," languages"," use"," gestures"," as"," a"," form"," of"," communication",","," and"," the"," study"," of"," these"," gestures"," can"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," cultures"," and"," societies"," in"," which"," they"," are"," used",".","\n","Overall",","," the"," study"," of"," gestures"," is"," a"," complex"," and"," multifaceted"," field"," that"," is"," constantly"," evolving","."," As"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," world"," and"," its"," cultures"," continues"," to"," evolve",","," so"," too"," will"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," gestures"," that"," are"," used"," to"," communicate"," within"," those"," cultures","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"cohere","label":1}